    "rationale": "Despite all 13 credibility factors showing achieved levels below required levels for MRL 5, and six factors flagged as unassessed epistemic gaps, the assessment team accepted the package on the basis that Monte Carlo UQ was performed and the hemolysis predictions fell below the absolute clinical threshold across all sampled operating points. The ContextOfUse does not declare an applicability constraint or operating envelope, leaving the boundary of valid model use unspecified; this is the targeted W-ON-02 weakness embedded in this adversarial sample.",
